channel.title: Help my computer keeps stuffing up (CMD, Task manager and Regedit disabled)
channel.description: Ok ive had this problem about 4 months now and its really anoying. Basically i keep getting an error when i try to run aryan or any other cmd program, task manager or regedit wont work either. Ive tried reinstalling widows with 3 different versions and it still keeps hapening. I think that its WGA (windows genuine activation tool) that keeps disabling it as each time i find records of it somewhere on my pc. Any help getting rid of it would be greatly apreciated, ive even tried norton but nothing came up.
